---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <main id="main-content">
    <div class="main-wrapper">
      <h1 aria-label="About">About me</h1>
      <p class="text-center">I make really fast websites</p>

      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16 text-left">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-800">
          Page builders in 2023 are awesome.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-left leading-relaxed">
          Nearly anyone can design a functioning and fashionable website for
          basically free.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-left leading-relaxed">
          The problem is that no-code tools can quickly paint non-programmers
          into a corner.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-left leading-relaxed">
          Bloated file sizes, clunky designs, and slow servers - kill
          conversions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-left leading-relaxed">
          Poor user experiences torpedo your traffic, and damage your <a
            class="text-skin-accent"
            href="https://baldmanbrands.com/blog/how-search-engines-punish"
          >
            credibility with Google</a
          >.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-left leading-relaxed">
          Google punishes bad websites by ranking them lower, while visitors
          simply cringe and leave.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-left leading-relaxed">
          If you want to build high-performance sites that cut through the
          clutter, I can show you how.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 text-center">
        <a
          class="mt-8 inline-flex justify-center rounded-lg text-sm font-bold py-3 px-4 bg-skin-card hover:bg-skin-card-muted text-skin-white"
          href="https://baldmanbrands.com/contact"
          ><span
            >Start for Free<!-- -->
            <span aria-hidden="true" class="hidden text-slate-400 sm:inline"
              >â†’</span
            ></span
          ></a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  #main-content {
    @apply mx-auto max-w-4xl pt-12;
  }
  .main-wrapper {
    @apply mb-14 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4;
  }
  .main-wrapper h1 {
    @apply text-4xl font-bold text-skin-accent;
  }
  .main-wrapper p {
    @apply mt-4 text-2xl sm:text-3xl;
  }
</style>
